% venv, mise

# Setup
```shell
echo 'eval "$(~/.local/bin/mise activate zsh)"' >> ~/.zshrc
```

# Install package
```shell
mise install <list_packages>
```

# List package
```shell
mise list
```

# Use Language for local
```shell
mise use <installed_packages>
```

# Use Language for global
```shell
mise use --global <installed_packages>
```

# Execute commands with specific tools
```shell
mise exec node@22 -- node -v
```

# Install npm package globally (like npm install -g)
```shell
mise use --global npm:<npm_package_name> # @anthropic-ai/claude-code
```


$ list_packages: mise ls-remote --all --- --fzf-overrides --tac

$ installed_packages: mise ls --installed | grep -v '^\s*$' | awk '{if (NF >= 2) print $1"@"$2}'
